    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear and character from its years on the road, it remains a solid, functional vehicle that offers great value. It\u2019s a perfect choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an accessible price point, with plenty of life left to give!",
